titleInfo.title: USA v. Stenger et al
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT as to Jeffrey A. Stenger (1). Defendant pleaded guilty to Count I of the Indictment and is committed to the custody of the Bureau of Prisons for a term of 60 months; 5 years supervised release with special conditions; $100 special assessment. Count II of the Indictment is dismissed on the motion of the United States as to this Defendant only. The Defendant shall surrender for service of sentence at the institution designated by the Bureauof Prisons no earlier than 2/19/2008 by 2:00 p.m., as to defendant Jeffrey A. Stenger. Ordered by Judge Laurie Smith Camp. (4 Certified copies to USM)(JAE, )
